{"type":"message","id":"05cf18bb","parentId":"b6575bae","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:00:27.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to execute a task from a cron configuration file. Let me first read the file to understand what needs to be done.\n\nThe file path is: ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md\n\nLet me read this file to understand the task requirements.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7012c8e6374745269f688aea","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773075620767}}
{"type":"message","id":"85618de6","parentId":"05cf18bb","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:00:27.603Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7012c8e6374745269f688aea","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 以下描述的文件都在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt；\n- 如果存在可用脚本，优先复用，不满足当前场景时才允许创建新脚本。\n- 执行时严格按照要求的文件名称及后缀，防止执行到不存在的文件。\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n2、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘，未收盘，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n3、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n4、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 3.1、满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 3.2、只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n5、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n6、使用openclaw message send --channel feishu --account stock --message xxx 命令，将数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给用户ID为：ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5的用户；\n7、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773075627601}}
{"type":"message","id":"c2f36641","parentId":"85618de6","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:00:31.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to understand the task. Let me read the related files to understand:\n1. get-data-template.md - for data format requirements\n2. alert-rules.md - for alert rules\n3. alert-template.md - for message template\n\nLet me read these files.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3cbc15ee633b4bc2a6592fd8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_337580cda0b9459f9b4d73a2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_404beec916614dd6bc78e922","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c4b25dce0daa453e98be0c71","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773075627603}}
{"type":"message","id":"a078146b","parentId":"c2f36641","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:00:31.754Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3cbc15ee633b4bc2a6592fd8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773075631753}}
{"type":"message","id":"f27bdd2a","parentId":"a078146b","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:00:31.757Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_337580cda0b9459f9b4d73a2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773075631755}}
{"type":"message","id":"a19499ea","parentId":"f27bdd2a","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:00:31.761Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_404beec916614dd6bc78e922","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773075631759}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e83cc4c","parentId":"a19499ea","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:00:31.764Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c4b25dce0daa453e98be0c71","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"代码 | 名称 | 现价 | 涨跌幅 | 成交量 | 成交额 | 时间\n601857|中国石油|12.92|+5.04%|817.45万|107.6亿|2026-03-10 00:54:19\n000852|石化机械|8.41|-3.33%|80.25万|7.1亿|2026-03-10 00:54:19\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773075631763}}
{"type":"message","id":"2be6a64c","parentId":"1e83cc4c","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:00:38.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I have the context. Now I need to:\n1. Check if there's a tushare-data skill available\n2. Get the watchlist stocks\n3. Check if market is closed (it's 1:00 AM Asia/Shanghai, so market should be closed)\n4. Get realtime data and check against alert rules\n\nLet me first check what skills are available and find the tushare-data skill. Also, I need to find the watchlist.\n\nLet me look for the tushare-data skill and the watchlist file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7ebb371a5ce644cd9bc987d7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_763861e61fec42e395ffb951","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills -name \"*tushare*\" -o -name \"*stock*\" 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773075631764}}
